arStrings.szText: Souls trapped within rotting corpses…This is the danger of the uninitiated tampering with necromancer magic.
Almost meditative, now that it's over.
The fool must have been desperate. Thought swallowing the finger would save him from death. A pity, but regardless, we have it now.
Shaking his head as he recounts what happened, then setting it aside to get on with what he needs to do.

The jeweled finger is vital to unlocking the gates of Necropolis. But I still must master the intricate rituals my mentor left me. It will take time, but you’ve played an integral role in reclaiming the holy city. Thank you.
